Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:05.52,italics,,0,0,0,,We've covered a third of our list,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.77,italics,,0,0,0,,but so far the Japanese government hasn’t made any response whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.22,italics,,0,0,0,,In any case,
