Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.33,italics,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.33,italics,,0,0,0,,Of all things at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.33,italics,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.18,italics,,0,0,0,,now that we have our secret weapon, \N
